___________Render Template_____________
Function that connect  html files to derver.py

Create a folder named "templates". Place html files in there. 

Codes to run render template______
@app.route('/')
def hello_world():
  return render_template(index.html)




___________Static File_____________
Files that never gonna change. They are static. 

Create a folder named "static". Place css anf javascripr files in there.

Make sure the following are correct in the server.py file. 
-- <link> ----> href= static/style.css
-- <script> ----> src= static/script.js
The files above must be referenced correctly since we changed the position of the files.

